As a Member, I want to book fitness classes, so that I can attend scheduled sessions  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Member shall select class type.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall display available time slots.//function  
    (User) 3. the Member shall confirm booking.//function  
    (System) 4. system shall reserve slot and send confirmation email.//function  
}  
Alternative Flow {  
    A. At any time, no slots are available :  
        1. system notify Class Full and suggest alternative sessions.
}  
}  

As a Member, I want to cancel a booking, so that I can free up my schedule  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Member shall select booked class.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall remove reservation and notify Trainer.//function  
}  
Alternative Flow {  
    A. At any time, cancellation is within two hours of class start :
        1. system charge five dollar late fee.
}  
}  

As a Trainer, I want to update class schedules, so that members see latest availability  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Trainer shall modify class time.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall update schedule and notify members.//function  
}  
}  

As a Front Desk, I want to register new members, so that they access gym facilities  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Front Desk shall input member details.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall generate membership ID.//function  
}  
} 

As a System Admin, I want to manage equipment records, so that maintenance is tracked  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the System Admin shall scan equipment barcodes.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall log maintenance dates.//function  
}  
}  

As a Member, I want to view attendance history, so that I track progress  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Member shall log into account.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall display attended classes.//function  
}  
}  

As a Trainer, I want to view class attendance, so that I adjust session difficulty  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Trainer shall select class.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall display participant names.//function  
}  
}  

As a Member, I want to upgrade membership, so that I unlock premium features  
{  
Basic Flow {  
    (User) 1. the Member shall select higher tier plan.//function  
    (System) 2. system shall process payment.//function  
}  
}